504
01:06:32.980 --> 01:06:34.670
This is executive council.

505
01:06:34.694 --> 01:06:36.377
Don't you shut me up.

506
01:06:36.401 --> 01:06:37.795
I have every right.

507
01:06:41.145 --> 01:06:42.962
Quiet. quiet.

508
01:06:42.986 --> 01:06:45.069
